metadata.name: Flower Zen Master
metadata.description:
The zen master sits meditating peacefully in a flower field with many different vibrantly colorful flowers. 

There are distant pastel mountains and clouds far away. 

A little rabbit in the zen master's arms, fluttering all around the zen master, are beautiful butterflies and little ladybugs among the flowers. 

When making this piece I wanted to wow the people who look at it with the detail and attention put into the flowers in the flower field, and make a lively yet peaceful scene. 

I hope as a viewer you feel that way.
